{"tid":2303813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"團購白米被指牟利，民政處扣起區議員6個月津貼","createTime":"2020-11-28T09:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T11:41:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6be6dec71cd09bbacd479f4fbbc10babb8726c6b","tid":2303813,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1.AeggwQwai28A2l1nU1mQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/ed4f9180-3133-11eb-a7c8-216c70ddc0ec\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1.AeggwQwai28A2l1nU1mQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-11%2Fed4f9180-3133-11eb-a7c8-216c70ddc0ec&h=d79eff52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由泛民主派主導的區議會與政府關係愈來愈惡劣，近日再有泛民區議員不獲民政事務署批營運津貼。屯門區議員張錦雄在社交網站貼文指，因曾為街坊提供團購白米服務，而遭民政事務處指他涉嫌阻街及無牌賣米，或牴觸《區議會條例》，更扣起6月至今的津貼，涉款超過6位數字。東網正向民政事務署查詢詳情。<br />\n<br />\n張錦雄的貼文指，疫情期間為協助有需要的街坊，故推出團購白米服務。坊間超級市場購買8公斤米需要110至130元，而向米商團購則可以80元購得。他最後以90元一包的價錢賣出，賺取的10元則會用作聘請「手足」搬米，及買米派給有需要的街坊。<br />\n<br />\n相關計劃在過去6個月內做進行了7輪，累積賣了近800多包米，當中派出137包愛心米予屯門鄉郊有需要家庭，涉款7萬多元，當中2700元聘請「手足」做兼職搬米派米。張錦雄強調，自己與職員或親屬並從中獲得任何利益。<br />\n<br />\n不過，他於7月收到民政處電郵，指有人投訴他阻街及無牌販賣食米，涉嫌牴觸《區議會條例》。他隨即回覆，要求與民政專員見面詳談，但一直未獲回應。而民政處亦扣起他6月至今的津貼，涉款超過6位數字，他批評民政處做法離譜，會考慮入稟小額錢債審裁處追討。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ShtI2JvBKYbO1QP1VZ3k.Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ0My4wNzY5MjMwNzY5MjMx/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/12848ff0-3134-11eb-a355-1e9ce20baacf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FShtI2JvBKYbO1QP1VZ3k.Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ0My4wNzY5MjMwNzY5MjMx%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-11%2F12848ff0-3134-11eb-a355-1e9ce20baacf&h=73152585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/團購白米被指牟利-民政處扣起區議員-6-個月津貼-044137116.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%9C%98%E8%B3%BC%E7%99%BD%E7%B1%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E7%89%9F%E5%88%A9-%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E8%99%95%E6%89%A3%E8%B5%B7%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-6-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC-044137116.html&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=3f338c83\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/團購白米被指牟利-民政處扣起區議員-6-個月津貼-044137116.html</a>"},{"pid":"6ac137f2e1c348289487d3a6a4cfa07496049a33","tid":2303813,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:03:27.000Z","msg":"民政狗準備用現金啦"},{"pid":"111268eb7d29aeaab776f12809c0c51184a90c81","tid":2303813,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced9de377656ef7176d60667a6a2fe685cc0f99a","tid":2303813,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:38:47.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"182e6d3f8d69bf68b3c54767b92b0b69e8494dbf","tid":2303813,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"躺著也中槍。。。。"},{"pid":"71c27de977ce9c06d8f750e7c4977f645b0ddb91","tid":2303813,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老母民政狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7adad3f56ec0ec3d631ab9f4574f81e266c0663","tid":2303813,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:44:33.000Z","msg":"百份報會幫民主派區議員出聲？"},{"pid":"a63cb0a86cf7edbc16923e062f5a897701cc23b7","tid":2303813,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:48:37.000Z","msg":"咁以前D旅行團呢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"